We met at 19 
4 apartments, many countries, oceans, national parks,  festivals and lives, here we are 11 years later, wow. 
Time flies when you’re having the best time 💕 
You’ve been with me on the best days of my life and on the sadest❤️‍🩹 you helped me through my grief, you make me laugh everyday, put me on the best music, and take me on the best adventures. I’m so grateful for the beautiful life we have created together, you’re the best person I know 🫀 me and polo(& our cutie fosters) love you so much. 
Swipe till the end for a picture from our first summer together in 2012 at Central Park, we went to almost 10 festivals that summer and just lived our lives spontaneously to the fullest. We still do now but more responsibly and with a bit less energy hehehe

The enchantment of burning man✨ 
So much gratitude for this place for teaching me the wisdom of navigating life's challenges and embracing the detour, letting go of control, plans and embracing everything that can unfold in the beauty that is this universe. 
May I continue to perceive its magic in every moment and place with my inner child present forever ❤️
1. Documenting my handmade and vintage sustainable outfits 
2. Night time adventures 
3. Climbing to the top of the highest art piece this year and being terrified on the top(face your fears) 
4. Sunrises with my love 
5. Details

7. Riding around during a dust storm to see art ✨
8. THE man and MY man 
9. Running into @gabz_w3trust at the post office (a highlight) ❤️❤️
10. EL PULPO 🐙
Immortalizing this here because is one of my favorite songs and my favorite sunrise set this year ❤️

The cotton candy sunsets, golden sunrises, the biggest full moon, the dust, the rain, the rainbows, the fire and even the mud played a role for the best year, a perfect symbiosis of the elements.
I experienced the power of manifestation like I never have before, literally speaking my wishes into existence  the same day if not the next? This place is a portal and you can not tell me otherwise 💫✨
The full moon was part of the experience too ❤️‍🔥
Our love language is DANCE, play and adventure(besides words of affirmation and physical touch of course 🥰). Didn’t think that after 11 years it could be possible to love you anymore but I DO❤️😉

One of our favorite day/nights that turned into the best morning🥹
I won the lottery at ashram galáctica and they made all my wishes come through and treated me and all my friends like royalty all night…was it even real? Im still a little bit in shock and so so grateful for this surreal and beautiful experience🥹 truly the most magical and special camp on playa✨
I wish I took more photos of their beautiful set up and amazing bar but the whole night was a dream and I was so overwhelmed with gratitude, luckily my friends snapped these 💕
Another testament that words are powerful and you can literally speak anything into existence ( and yes being a little delusional is part of it too hehe) luckiest girl in the world❤️✨♾️

social_posts.post_text:
This morning, right as the storm was brewing, the sky parted just for us, painting yet another serendipitous moment of our week in front of the temple. 
Later that day, the storm created the perfect opportunity for us to unwind, treasure the memories, and contemplate the enchantment of the night and morning. 
Following a blissful 24-hour cuddly slumber, as if by fate, a double rainbow graced the sky—an incredible sight rarely seen at Burning Man. 
These fortunate events shaped our journey, serving as a living testament to our enduring love story ❤️♾️
For more details of the story, we’ll tell you in person😊
